information: The company KLAAS + PITSCH FLEISCH- UND WURSTWAREN GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1971, which operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industry. It also operates in the Fish, Meat, Offal, and Dairy products industries. It is based in Freudenberg, Germany.
